didn't actually matter because it was all fate it was all driven by by circumstance so you can see he's in this he's in an area of uh of tremendous fermentation a bit like today really i mean today if you look at the human race all over the place so you get this get this feeling that there was a lot of investigation going on about you know the purpose of life and so uh

