139
00:15:31,666 --> 00:15:34,928
which you want to scratch and then it disappears.

140
00:15:36,309 --> 00:15:42,395
There's nothing substantial about it at all, except that we give it a substantiality by saying it's me.

141
00:15:43,277 --> 00:15:49,903
So something happens with the body and the heart whenever we turn it into something that I am.

142
00:15:51,244 --> 00:15:52,705
And it's impossible to escape.

143
00:15:53,105 --> 00:15:56,408
As soon as I say to myself, oh, I'm depressed, that's it, isn't it?

144
00:15:57,308 --> 00:16:00,272
