145
00:16:01,062 --> 00:16:03,645
It's like Prozac, isn't it?

146
00:16:03,686 --> 00:16:06,870
There's no escape from I am depressed.

147
00:16:07,532 --> 00:16:08,572
Worse is I am happy.

148
00:16:09,475 --> 00:16:12,619
