151
00:16:15,683 --> 00:16:16,004
See?

152
00:16:16,024 --> 00:16:27,761
So this process of identifying with it, identifying with the emotional state, gives it some sort of solidity, some sort of permanency, some sort of reality.

153
00:16:28,163 --> 00:16:32,089
