154
00:16:32,690 --> 00:16:33,912
It's just a feeling.

155
00:16:34,913 --> 00:16:37,096
Mental feeling, maybe, but it's just a feeling.

156
00:16:38,759 --> 00:16:40,802
And even more fleeting are these thoughts.

157
00:16:41,384 --> 00:16:45,188
So when we see these thoughts come and go, most times we're caught up in them.

158
00:16:46,532 --> 00:16:51,318
