191
00:19:07,413 --> 00:19:10,757
There was this change of way of looking at things.

192
00:19:11,142 --> 00:19:18,589
We can only imagine that, having been to all these teachers, he was in a bit of a state of despair, really, because there was no answer.

193
00:19:19,652 --> 00:19:21,192
